snippet.title: Yeah Jam Fury:  U, Me, Everybody! Trailer 1
snippet.description:
GET THE MANGO! Yeah Jam Fury tests your speed and ingenuity in over 100 levels of smiling face blocks. Utilize all three of your egos to create blocks, scale walls, and destroy everything in the way of your righteous fruit.

Catch Yeah Jam Fury: U, Me, Everybody! when it launches on Steam this December 2017!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/633930/Yeah_Jam_Fury_U_Me_Everybody/
http://wes-plus.com/yeahjamfury/
